---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---
<MainLayout title="Stat Breakpoints | ers">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="flex-col">
    <h2>Stat Breakpoints</h2>

    <section>
      <h3>What are breakpoints?</h3>
      <p>Breakpoints are points in stat allocations in which leveling past 
      certain numbers end in 
      <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diminishing_returns">
        <em>Diminishing Returns</em>
      </a>.
      </p>
      <p> This means that when making an <strong>"optimal/efficient"</strong> 
      build, you should take these points into account.
      </p>
      <p>For example: Leveling Strength from 80 to 82, is <strong>less</strong>
      efficient than leaving it at 80, and using those 2 points elsewhere.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section">
      <div class="flex-col">
        <h3>General Build Advice</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Get Vigor to 60. Just get it to 60. Seriously.</li>
          <li>10 Mind is fine for melee users</li>
          <li>~30 Endurance is fine for most builds</li>
          <li>Pick 1 damage Stat to max:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>Strength</li>
              <li>Dexterity</li>
              <li>Intelligence</li>
              <li>Faith</li>
              <li>Arcane</li>
            </ul>
          <li>After RL125-150, you can choose a second damage stat:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>Strength/Faith (good heals & self-buffs)</li>
              <li>Dexterity/Arcane (good bleed damage/weapons)</li>
              <li>Intelligence/Faith (full caster)</li>
              <li>Strength/Dexterity (Quality)</li>
            </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-col">
        <h3>Endgame Rune Level</h3>
        <p>Changes depending on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>How much side (optional) content you do</li>
          <li>How much you farm for runes</li>
          <li>How much you die</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Typical rune level around endgame is around <strong>130-180</strong>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  * {
    --bg: #16141f;
    --muted: #6e6a86;
    --subtle: #908caa;
    --text: #e0def4;
    --love: #eb6f92;
    --gold: #f6c177;
    --rose: #ebbcba;
    --pine: #31748f;
    --foam: #9ccfd8;
    --iris: #c4a7e7;
  }
  .flex-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  h2 {
    color: var(--rose);
    font-size: 3rem;
  }
  h3 {
    color: var(--love);
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: 2rem;
  }
  .split-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 1.5rem;
  }
  a {
    color: var(--foam);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  ul {
    padding-inline: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
</style>
